The '''Quarren Sector''' was a large area in [[Crevasse City (Kalkovak)|Crevasse City]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Kalkovak]]. The area was populated with [[Quarren/Legends|Quarren]] and was a popular settlement for the [[Species/Legends|species]] outside of [[Dac/Legends|Mon Calamari]]. [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]] once searched the area for [[Illyan Webble]] who knew the location of the [[Yavin Vassilika]]. However he had hitched a ride to Mon Calamari prior to their visit.

